                                <h1>David P. Boder Interviews Charlotte Schultze; September 20, 1946; MÃ¼nchen, Germany</h1>
                                            <ul class="transcripts">
    <li class="interview_home">
        <a href="interviewee?doc=schultzeC">
            Interview homepage
        </a>
